Probability is the foundation for ML algorithms like Naive Bayes, classification, risk prediction.

Topic	Meaning
Probability	Chance of event
Event	Something happening
Independent event	One event does not affect another
Dependent event	One event affects another
Conditional probability	Probability based on condition
